node.text: This is such a cute idea! Love it!

❤️Hearty Meals right to your doorstep with Saveur group’s latest launch- their online food delivery store - shop.saveur.sg offering Islandwide Delivery. With this one-stop-shop, they are offering Signature dishes & Ice Cream from their 4 Concepts namely @saveursg , @mediumraresg , @frapasbar and @breadandbutterflysg .⁣
⁣
We had their mussels and fries, their signature duck confit and shredded duck bowl!! ❤️❤️ Had such a delicious meal in the comfort of my own home! Good News!! You can get 10% off your order with promo code SHER10OFF on TOP of ongoing promos all the way till June! So what are you waiting for 💗⁣
⁣
